<para style="q1">

<verse number="11" style="v" />This was because they had rebelled against God's word</para>

<para style="q1">and rejected the instruction of the Most High.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="12" style="v" />He humbled their hearts through hardship;</para>

<para style="q1">they stumbled and there was no one to help them up.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="13" style="v" />Then they called out to Yahweh in their trouble,</para>

<para style="q1">and he brought them out of their distress.</para>
